  <h1>Chicken Biriyani</h1>
  <p>This is very tasty ,spicy and your Favourite Chicken Biriyani!This will be ready in few minutes and get ready to taste the famous dish of the world</p>

  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>300 grams chicken</li>
    <li>3 cups soaked seeraga samba Rice</li>
    <li>4-5 tbsp penaut oil</li>
    <li>2 finely chopped onions</li>
    <li>2 chopped Tomatoes</li>
    <li>3 split green chillies</li>
    <li>1/2 cup mint leaves</li>
    <li>1 tbsp Ginger garlic taste</li>
    <li>2 tbsp curd or Youghurt</li>
    <li>salt to taste</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Instructions</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>wash and soak rice for 20 minutes,then cook it until it is 70% done and set aside</li>
    <li>Heat oil in large pot and sout onions and until it golden bown</li>
    <li>Add ginger garlic paste and cook it until, Raw smell disappears</li>
    <li>Add the chicken pieces,salt,spieces and Tomatoes then cook until the chicken is tender</li>
    <li>cover  on the pot on low dump,for 15 minutes</li>
    <li>Gently mix and serve hot with raita or salad. ğŸ—ğŸš</li>
    </ol>
